Fire in Russia's mental hospital kills at least 36: authorities
2013-04-26 00:53:40 GMT
A big fire broke out in a mental hospital in Russia's Moscow region early Friday, killing at least 36 people and injuring many others, the Russian emergency department said.The ITAR-TASS news agency reported earlier that rescuers found at least 12 bodies.
